23 Section 4. Section 13-2-402, MCA, is amended to read:
24 "13-2-402. Reasons for cancellation. The election administrator shall cancel the registration of an
25 elector if:
26 (1) the elector submits a written request for cancellation;
27 (2) a certificate of the death of the elector is filed or if the elector is reported to the election
28 administrator as deceased by the department of public health and human services in the department's reports
